hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I like watching TV noguchimedres.org And again the myth continues with your last statement. Though numerous examples of people being killed exist on film not once in history is there one example of a true snuff film , it is a damn urban legend.That you put it at the end of a news report that readers expect to be fully factual is irresponsible at best to willful lying at the most. C'mon , you are supposed to be better than that you are Time not the Enquirer spouting off about Bat Boy or some other trash.
